{"tid":1002722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州學生：來港7天參觀香港5間大學，食堂是打卡點","createTime":"2019-01-31T07:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T08:59:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c5fbaf5eaa1b4765d4799e7c87566a2127e1fe2d","tid":1002722,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190131145204\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190131145204&h=99b743bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地「鴨仔團」近日攻陷香港多間大學。東網記者今午(31日)到中文大學校園視察，在新亞書院學生飯堂發現有內地高中生團正在用膳，約佔用6至7張飯枱。 <br />\n<br />\n來自廣州的高二生涂同學表示，正參加一個冬令營，來港7天參觀香港5間大學，包括港大、中大、理大、城大及科大。他稱，該團由幾名老師帶領約40名來自廣州不同高中的學生，到不同大學聽講座，參觀實驗室，「食堂也是我們必須打卡的點。」據他所知，該團每年會舉辦2次，現時已辦至第16期，明年參加高考的他表示，參觀香港各大學後，很可能會來港升學。 <br />\n<br />\n中大工商管理二年級學生謝同學表示，平日下午在他所屬的新亞書院不時有「鴨仔團」出沒，主要為內地中小學生，「天人合一、新亞canteen(學生飯堂)都會見到。」他指，飯堂經常會被「鴨仔團」霸去大量位置，中大學生「好難搵位食飯」，甚至要行去較遠的飯堂用膳。他指學生團比較嘈吵，平時出入宿舍都會受到滋擾，而車路亦常被多部旅遊巴堵塞。 <br />\n<br />\n中大一年級學生譚同學及魏同學曾見過內地學生團「一車車咁送入嚟」，飯堂亦被他們霸佔多張飯枱。魏指出，有時會有大批人塞在主要路口，或會阻礙一些正趕往課堂的學生，但他認為中大始終是對外開放，有遊客參觀無可厚非，但希望校方會提醒遊客部分飯堂是學生及教職員專用，遊人應去其他接待校外遊客的餐廳。譚認為，校方應做好疏導人流的措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190131145204\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190131145204&h=c1a9ea97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131104547414-0131_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190131143341\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131104547414-0131_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190131143341&h=8f837526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131104547414-0131_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190131143341\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131104547414-0131_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190131143341&h=d79ddc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/photo/bkn-20190131104547414-0131_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190131143341\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190131104547414-0131_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190131143341&h=56b8b929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/bkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fbkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6qjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=07f134c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/bkn-20190131140857469-0131_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f412325cca1b960bfaa35462492c1e4ffa6ad508","tid":1002722,"uid":19126,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"見到都覺得又臭又嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c0cb39e6e78e4ea8530151184a8040fd715c1d","tid":1002722,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fefb1ed4bb52a76033c2cedbf869a9aaf946291","tid":1002722,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜唔去埋啲豪宅區"},{"pid":"321fbf0b6de0f150674cf